command_group: az security security-connector devops githubowner repo

commands.name: az security security-connector devops githubowner repo list
commands.summary: List GitHub repositories onboarded to the connector.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops githubowner repo list --name
                                                            --owner-name
                                                            --resource-group
                                                            [--max-items]
                                                            [--next-token]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops githubowner repo show
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops githubowner repo show [--ids]
                                                            [--name]
                                                            [--owner-name]
                                                            [--repo-name]
                                                            [--resource-group]
                                                            [--subscription]
